>(WAFERID|POSTPOS 1 POS) and verify the correct parameters are set.<
>The wafer ID or the Post Position were SET but not STORED then the robot<
>was rebooted. User STORE ALIGNER command to store parameters.<
>The robot was reset after the wafer ID or Post Position was SET.<
>The aligner retained the setting	 however	 the robot lost the information.<
>Reset the robot and the aligner at the same time.<
>
